text: Jelenča () is one of the boroughs of Šabac City in the Mačva District of Serbia. The borough has a Serb ethnic majority. In the 2002 census, its population was found to be 1,803 people. ==See also== *List of places in Serbia *Mačva Category:Mačva Category:Populated places in Mačva District
title: Jelenča
